### 1. Đăng nhập ADMIN (Bắt buộc dùng acc Admin)
POST http://localhost:9999/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin@smartmoney.vn",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "deviceToken": "device_token_admin",
  "deviceType": "Web",
  "deviceName": "Admin PC"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 2. Lấy danh sách User (Phân trang & Tìm kiếm)
GET http://localhost:9999/api/admin/users?page=0&size=10&search=minh
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 3. Lấy danh sách User (Lọc theo trạng thái Locked)
GET http://localhost:9999/api/admin/users?locked=true
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 4. Lấy thống kê Dashboard
GET http://localhost:9999/api/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 5. Khóa tài khoản User
# Thay ID 100 bằng ID user muốn khóa
PUT http://localhost:9999/api/admin/users/100/lock
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 6. Mở khóa tài khoản User
PUT http://localhost:9999/api/admin/users/100/unlock
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}